If you had a string of
say length 20 centimeters,

00:06:10.787 --> 00:06:12.970
and you put one focus
there and one focus there

00:06:12.970 --> 00:06:15.454
and you kind of put your
chalk in the string,

00:06:15.454 --> 00:06:17.196
and you just tried to move it around,

00:06:17.196 --> 00:06:19.634
and so it would look something,

00:06:19.634 --> 00:06:21.955
it would look something like that.

